item.title: Great open-access data sets of public interest
item.description: 1 Data 1.1 Licences 1.2 General 1.3 Environment 1.4 Health 1.5 Psychology 1 Data This posts lists some great open-access data sets of public or broad interest. This list is by no means comprehensiv, it’s just a casual curation of interesting sources. Note that this post is not updated, so more frequent releases than documented here are possible. You’ll find both links to repositories as well as to particular datasets, in no special order.
